{"tid":289276,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[拒絕遺忘6.23見] 毋忘沙士抗疫英雄","createTime":"2017-06-19T00:30:37.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-23T16:41:28.000Z","uid":9348,"like":111,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"04b234ec5bf3c05e9285619507e51750a7cee59a","tid":289276,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T00:30:37.000Z","msg":"毋忘沙士抗疫英雄<br />\n日期：六月二十三曰<br />\n時間：下午七時半至八時半<br />\n地點：香港公園<br />\n流程：<br />\n七時半 － 自發市民將於太極園派發自行印製之單張，上面刊有當年歷史，供出席者回顧抗疫事蹟。期間市民可到抗疫英雄紀念碑前獻花。同時亦有影片及照片投影，以及英雄生平回顧。<br />\n八時十分 － 自由獻花，其後以默哀作結<br />\n<br />\n主辦單位：無。鼓勵公眾自發參與和派發單張。<br />\n注意事項：誠邀熱心市民自備傳單或鮮花到現場派發，亦歡迎市民無分地點，當晚八時半一同悼念。<br />\n<br />\n**************************************************************************<br />\n二零零三年，沙士疫症蔓延香港，幸得一眾醫護人員，緊守崗位，得以戰勝疫病。 二零零三年六月二十三日，世界衛生組織終從疫區名單剔除香港，香港人戰勝沙士的標誌一步，惟沙士疫症累計奪走二百九十九位港人寶貴生命，當中八位為醫護人員。是次活動希望藉六二三的歷史意義，重提當年抗疫歷史，紀念殉職之醫護人員外，亦感激抗疫時間香港全體醫護人員的無私付出，藉此呼籲香港人尊重並銘記歷史，毋負他們的付出和犧牲。<br />\n<br />\n我們將準備少量單張和鮮花，力量雖少，希望在此呼籲大家自發參與，有心人士可自備載有當年歷史的單張或鮮花到場派發，讓公眾可以重溫歷史，緬懷過去。我們堅信香港人不會愧對英靈，讓歷史從公眾認知中湮滅，往後不須架設高台，不限時間和地點，香港人都會本著良知，自發悼念，銘記救人事蹟，並將他們無私奉獻的精神傳承今後所有香港人。<br />\n<br />\n英雄無名，謹此向香港所有無私付出的醫護人員致敬。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/082823_fb12b3c22e352470c8f02647d52bcd76.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F082823_fb12b3c22e352470c8f02647d52bcd76.jpg&h=9732ab10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKSarsHeroes/posts/120774511840174:0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKSarsHeroes%2Fposts%2F120774511840174%3A0&d=nRBCArb6Vd4Iu1%2ByI8vYj1KzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=7341d7f0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKSarsHeroes/posts/120774511840174:0</a>"},{"pid":"ffe81915d42f36d26ec890a322c7cbebc9f35bd3","tid":289276,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T00:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce45ba093f338cb67c79c88bcd47aa91dcb6e6e6","tid":289276,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T00:39:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1cf05bdfbb436362373fa0c95d876cd7cb69831","tid":289276,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T00:53:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有既"},{"pid":"fb2c7803f3bc14c9f24617ba80e43c260e77ab5d","tid":289276,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T02:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"961500df9d54b818b66b7c80c4ccc886c25a5487","tid":289276,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T02:14:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb34bcedd04e014911594bea8179860ef0bf1d86","tid":289276,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T02:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e358320a13a1e0756645608d5066b1bc42dc531c","tid":289276,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T03:50:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43f6d6400c290788d9da1e626fb3ab8a5fc21fab","tid":289276,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T04:02:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7fe7bc165ffbe7ac36009722875cf0d669d9f7","tid":289276,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:20:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84436e20bfa8f470302078095df1044ac86d9e9a","tid":289276,"uid":9348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T05:46:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/19/134640_c70720c6987df5382fab6729e6879a06.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F19%2F134640_c70720c6987df5382fab6729e6879a06.jpg&h=5ccd1592&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【抗疫英雄列傳 一 劉大鈞醫生】<br />\n<br />\n劉大鈞醫生為私家執業的兒科醫生，享年五十六歲， 逝世時遺下妻子及一名正攻讀大學醫科課程的女兒，生前其診所位於尖沙嘴東英大廈，偶爾亦往醫院為病人施行手術。<br />\n<br />\n劉醫生的朋友憶述，他為人處處先為別人設想，對病人、小朋友尤其關心，亦指出劉醫生總是「太搏命」，為病人奔波而不遺餘力。<br />\n<br />\n劉醫生沙士爆發前期在診所接觸一名持續多日發燒的病人，並將之轉介至瑪嘉烈醫院，惟醫院當時拒絕接受該名病人，劉醫生親自送她入私家醫院，繼續為其診症，疑在此期間受感染。及後劉醫生於三月二十日病發，兩天後到瑪嘉烈醫院求診，與病魔搏鬥十三日後，於四月三日宣告不治，享年五十六歲。劉醫生遺孀程氏亦於探病期間感染非典型肺炎，所幸留院兩個月後病癮。在官員仍未承認沙士在港擴散之前，劉大鈞醫生成為首名死於非典型肺炎的醫護人員。"},{"pid":"d6d8a289994179aa2627e7581ca881a21a0a876c","tid":289276,"uid":49004,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T07:24:27.000Z","msg":"冇人理架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n張德江隱瞞疫情 <br />\n大陸人食染病果子狸搞到爆發SARS 之後由大陸人傳SARS落黎香港<br />\n搞到香港人299死 3千幾人染病 食特敏福搞到骨枯後遺症"},{"pid":"d23820092ea2f4f1b0b088a16dd4f673711a4849","tid":289276,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T10:43:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62565c4669024daedc12f3f325f76c7a683f9eeb","tid":289276,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:21:49.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"2c5dbcc418604c42486af7b6126d905ad73841e0","tid":289276,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T11:33:53.000Z","msg":"唔會有人理架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d7f8992abe7f413f636b405d12e05d38cd60a2","tid":289276,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:43:27.000Z","msg":"張德肛"},{"pid":"a37340a9a9edf9847923f267a62d0fa69ed8dbcf","tid":289276,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:55:59.000Z","msg":"邊撚個仆街畀負皮同我死出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c0d9505cb538e8107b324a736e9aba5b58715c","tid":289276,"uid":120051,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T12:59:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0361a4b494f8af3a44d2da1653832039fb034f7b","tid":289276,"uid":26672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:04:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>已經十四年lu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />時間過得好快</blockquote><br />\n係，嗰陣三年級仲傻更更以為有假放好開心，原來就係香港最霉最差嘅日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dfc4378730d1449bd7afeefd2142ba7839027ed","tid":289276,"uid":123440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T13:05:36.000Z","msg":"諗吓宵夜食乜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d052b1226769f8c1b9241b9dc74b9316b84deed","tid":289276,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:19:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇人理架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n張德江隱瞞疫情 <br />\n大陸人食染病果子狸搞到爆發SARS 之後由大陸人傳SARS落黎香港<br />\n搞到香港人299死 3千幾人染病 食特敏福搞到骨枯後遺症</blockquote><br />\n張德江提沙士「共同抗疫」　沙士互助會會長批不盡不實　「香港人靠自己抗疫」<br />\n立場報道2016/5/18 &mdash; 9:32<br />\n<br />\n2003年時任廣東省委書記、被指有份隱瞞疫情的人大委員長張德江，昨甫抵香港便主動提起沙士，指自己與港府共同抗擊非典型肺炎疫情並取得勝利。沙士互助會會長林志釉今日在商台節目批評，張的說法不盡不實，「佢完全無幫，難聽啲講，就連累香港。」<br />\n<br />\n沙士互助會會長林志釉指出，整個抗疫工作只是靠香港人自己，「香港人要係靠自己的醫護人員、兩間大學、所有市民去抗疫，我唔明白張先生點解話共同抗疫，佢亦都無交代到點解整整幾個月時間，疫情在廣東省入面爆發，佢完全無將資料帶到香港，等香港有一啲準備去抗疫。」<br />\n<br />\n林志釉指出，時任特首董建華委托的專家報告，已確認疫情早已出現，但2003年1月廣東省疫情報告，亦無交予世衛及香港，「香港白白錯失時機，去做好預防措施。」"},{"pid":"88318abc5f4c9f11176552961a1434dca10f810b","tid":289276,"uid":9348,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:21:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔會有人理架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n香港人寧願去六四邪壇拜鄰国死人都唔理為港捐軀既真英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0897d9d6e30b1bff83dd6289ece5f86c5421092","tid":289276,"uid":8858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:23:00.000Z","msg":"去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bbf3b1d134593c93f5f659b940740985e6ef83c","tid":289276,"uid":35774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:26:11.000Z","msg":"張德江<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36730267c0e3e057622de445b80fcb409d159326","tid":289276,"uid":36673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T14:50:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82b793d76fc05b31c334b0eb829252f499ea47f6","tid":289276,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:11:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2c0f3d6e11aa5b1cecfe6773e4e0d4bae972088","tid":289276,"uid":72277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T15:19:01.000Z","msg":"毋忘抗疫英雄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a80bc0e5499dc14cccc36f74b16b62691d0eb20","tid":289276,"uid":3659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit